• Female survival rate: {female_rate}%
• Male survival rate: {male_rate}%

The data shows a dramatic difference in survival between sexes:
- Females had {female_survivors - male_survivors} more survivors than males
- The female survival rate was {female_rate - male_rate:.1f} percentage points higher than males

